    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook, covered, for a further 4-5 min</p>",
