    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, add your <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 7 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>macaroni</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
