    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong>,<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>and<strong> </strong>a pinch of<strong> salt </strong> – these are your<strong> smoky breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar flavour block</strong></p>",
